# Navigate Peptides — Brand & Design System

> Source of truth: Client Direction page + approved mockups. Do not deviate.

## Design Philosophy

Premium biotech-style brand. Minimal, controlled, high-end. Strong scientific credibility. A knowledge authority, not just a supplier. Dark, matte, low-saturation throughout.

## Colors

### Base
```css
--nav-brand-green: #2A3B36;        /* Primary brand — backgrounds, panels */
```

### Text
```css
--nav-text-primary: #EAEAEA;        /* Primary text */
--nav-text-secondary: #A8B0AD;      /* Secondary/supporting */
```

### Category Colors (Client-Approved Final)

One color per category. Same color for: vial cap band, mg text, thin accent line, site badges.

| Category | Color Name | HEX |
|----------|-----------|-----|
| Metabolic Research | Deep Cognitive Blue | `#2F4666` |
| Tissue Repair Research | Repair Gold | `#9C843E` |
| Cognitive Research | Longevity Violet | `#5E507F` |
| Inflammation Research | Advanced Wine | `#4A141C` |
| Cellular Research | Cellular Rose | `#8E5660` |
| Dermal Research | Dermal Green | `#4A6B5F` |
| Research Blends | Elite Graphite | `#474C50` |

### Color Rules
- One color per category — never mix
- No gradients
- Matte / low saturation only
- Consistent across vial, product page accent, category card, catalog tag

