## Typography

```css
:root {
  --nav-font-display: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;     /* Hero headlines */
  --nav-font-body: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;        /* Body, UI, nav */
  --nav-font-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', 'SF Mono', monospace;    /* CAS numbers, batch IDs */
}
```

### Patterns
- **Kicker labels:** All-caps Inter, wide letter-spacing, accent color, left-border line
- **Hero headline:** Large Playfair Display, warm white
- **Section headings:** All-caps Inter, centered, wide tracking
- **Body text:** Inter, secondary text color
- **Technical data:** JetBrains Mono
- **Buttons:** All-caps Inter, outlined (not filled), letter-spaced

## Components

### Navigation
```
[◇ NAVIGATE PEPTIDES]    Compounds    Research    Quality    About    [Request Access]
```

### Hero (Homepage)
- Left: Kicker → Serif headline → Body text → Two outlined CTAs
- Right: Product vial photo (dark, moody) + Product Info overlay card

### Category Cards (7-card grid)
Each: illustration, title, description, "VIEW" button, category color accent

### Trust Signals (3 items, centered with icons)
1. THIRD-PARTY TESTED
2. LABORATORY USE ONLY
3. GMP COMPLIANT MANUFACTURING

### Buttons
Outlined only. Not filled. ~4px radius. Uppercase, letter-spaced.

### Footer
Three columns (Company, Research Directory, Resources) + RUO disclaimer + copyright

## Imagery
- Product photography: dark, moody lighting, category color on cap band
- Category illustrations: molecular structures, microscopy, cellular imagery
- Icons: simple line-art, thin stroke
- NO stock lab photos. NO human imagery. NO before/after.

